{"vv22:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv22:0.2":"Itthivimana ","vv22:0.3":"Cittalatavagga ","vv22:0.4":"5. Bhadditthivimanavatthu ","vv22:1.1":"“Nila pita ca kala ca, ","vv22:1.2":"manjittha atha lohita; ","vv22:1.3":"Uccavacanam vannanam, ","vv22:1.4":"kinjakkhaparivarita. ","vv22:2.1":"Mandaravanam pupphanam, ","vv22:2.2":"malam dharesi muddhani; ","vv22:2.3":"Nayime annesu kayesu, ","vv22:2.4":"rukkha santi sumedhase. ","vv22:3.1":"Kena kayam upapanna, ","vv22:3.2":"tavatimsam yasassini; ","vv22:3.3":"Devate pucchitacikkha, ","vv22:3.4":"kissa kammassidam phalan”ti. ","vv22:4.1":"“Bhadditthikati mam annamsu, ","vv22:4.2":"Kimilayam upasika; ","vv22:4.3":"Saddha silena sampanna, ","vv22:4.4":"Samvibhagarata sada. ","vv22:5.1":"Acchadananca bhattanca, ","vv22:5.2":"senasanam padipiyam; ","vv22:5.3":"Adasim ujubhutesu, ","vv22:5.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","vv22:6.1":"Catuddasim pancadasim, ","vv22:6.2":"ya ca pakkhassa atthami; ","vv22:6.3":"Patihariyapakkhanca, ","vv22:6.4":"atthangasusamagatam. ","vv22:7.1":"Uposatham upavasissam, ","vv22:7.2":"sada silesu samvuta; ","vv22:7.3":"Sannama samvibhaga ca, ","vv22:7.4":"vimanam avasamaham. ","vv22:8.1":"Panatipata virata, ","vv22:8.2":"musavada ca sannata; ","vv22:8.3":"Theyya ca aticara ca, ","vv22:8.4":"majjapana ca araka. ","vv22:9.1":"Pancasikkhapade rata, ","vv22:9.2":"Ariyasaccana kovida; ","vv22:9.3":"Upasika cakkhumato, ","vv22:9.4":"Appamadaviharini; ","vv22:9.5":"Katavasa katakusala tato cuta, ","vv22:9.6":"Sayampabha anuvicarami nandanam. ","vv22:10.1":"Bhikkhu caham paramahitanukampake, ","vv22:10.2":"Abhojayim tapassiyugam mahamunim; ","vv22:10.3":"Katavasa katakusala tato cuta, ","vv22:10.4":"Sayampabha anuvicarami nandanam. ","vv22:11.1":"Atthangikam aparimitam sukhavaham, ","vv22:11.2":"Uposatham satatamupavasim aham; ","vv22:11.3":"Katavasa katakusala tato cuta, ","vv22:11.4":"Sayampabha anuvicarami nandanan”ti. ","vv22:12.1":"Bhadditthivimanam pancamam. "}